{"tid":1506114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咩方法都好，唔好再被捕","createTime":"2019-08-25T17:08:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T06:00:26.000Z","uid":44298,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b6e6d5c782cbde4a13289d40306997ae87df85bc","tid":1506114,"uid":44298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:08:54.000Z","msg":"有post話有人俾人打到入icu，可以知道，你一俾人拉果刻，你嘅人生<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">已完</span></span>。你有好大機會殘廢，昏迷，甚至死亡。<br />\n<br />\n前線嘅大家，從今以後請你地記得以上嘅一段話，一定要救人，同埋反抗。我以前都好和理非，而家覺得，喺對家唔會死嘅情況下，你地打機出咩魔法我地都唔會再有怨言。<br />\n<br />\n體能唔好同埋冇膽嘅，希望你地唔好走咁前。<br />\n<br />\n（利申：體能超差，唔會上前害人害己。）"},{"pid":"49330394ee74551193fba88853e3345cf8daee49","tid":1506114,"uid":233929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:14:19.000Z","msg":"係呀，只要團火不熄，今日贏唔到仲有下次<br />\n不被捕，不受傷先係首要呀手足"},{"pid":"c9614170977849d2e4a079b62d6559a1c570ed20","tid":1506114,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:31:52.000Z","msg":"政府冇底線咁欺壓人民<br />\n人民亦無需有底線反抗<br />\n<br />\n石頭與火 從來都係對抗極權 開拓未來嘅象徵<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505886</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n全部九龍灣嘅前線入哂黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502833</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"356bfb4f880a1f3ed69df670304c7e577c67218d","tid":1506114,"uid":158404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:33:48.000Z","msg":"推 唔好再塞住勇武喇 勇武唔會推你，會自己死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9e1843780611ac350ed3b6520e7e22bde045ae","tid":1506114,"uid":289474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:53:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一定要救人，反抗！</span><br />\n喺對家唔會死嘅情況下，用盡一切方法反抗！<br />\n手足一個都不能少！！！please <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face